OL,3,CWhite House press dinner shooting:
OL,4,CTrump was remarkably calm and good
OL,5,Chumoured
OL,7,FI arrived at the White House as the
OL,8,Fsecurity operation was still in full
OL,9,Fswing last night. The shots fired at
OL,10,Fthe White House Correspondents' dinner
OL,11,Fhad radically shifted one of the most
OL,12,Fglamorous evenings in the DC calendar.
OL,14,FI watched from a few feet away as the
OL,15,Fpresident entered the press briefing
OL,16,Froom, less crowded than normal.
OL,18,FThe president and First Lady were
OL,19,Fthere with his press secretary
OL,20,FKaroline Leavitt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
