OL,3,CWhite House press dinner shooting:
OL,4,CTrump was remarkably calm and good
OL,5,Chumoured
OL,7,FSo too the head of the FBI Kash Patel
OL,8,Fand other members of his cabinet.
OL,10,FThis was a deliberate show of unity
OL,11,Fand resolve, so soon after a gunman
OL,12,Fhad tried to breach the security of
OL,13,Fthe gala dinner where the president
OL,14,Fhad been guest of honour.
OL,16,FDonald Trump was remarkably calm and
OL,17,Fgood humoured as he spoke.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
