OL,3,CWhite House press dinner shooting:
OL,4,CTrump was remarkably calm and good
OL,5,Chumoured
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FHe attempted to strike a tone of unity
OL,13,Fat one point and was clear in his
OL,14,Fdetermination that the dinner would be
OL,15,Frescheduled, saying he had asked for
OL,16,Fit to carry on last night.
OL,18,FHe also did not seek to make political
OL,19,Fcapital from the incident, making it
OL,20,Fclear this did not appear to be linked
OL,21,Fto the war in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
