OL,3,CWhite House press dinner shooting:
OL,4,CTrump was remarkably calm and good
OL,5,Chumoured
OL,7,FThe attempted shooting took place in
OL,8,Fthe same hotel where President Ronald
OL,9,FReagan was shot in 1981. When asked
OL,10,Fabout the repeated political violence
OL,11,Fwhich has dogged this country down the
OL,12,Fyears, Donald Trump seemed to be
OL,13,Fsanguine.
OL,15,FHe repeated his story about how
OL,16,Fdangerous being a president is in the
OL,17,Fmodern era, claiming about eight per
OL,18,Fcent of incumbents are shot at,
OL,19,Fagreeing it's the cost of doing
OL,20,Fbusiness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
