OL,3,CWhite House press dinner shooting:
OL,4,CTrump was remarkably calm and good
OL,5,Chumoured
OL,7,F"I like not to think about it," he
OL,8,Fsaid. "I think I handle it as well as
OL,9,Fit can be handled."
OL,11,FHe spoke of his shock describing the
OL,12,Fnoise of gunfire which he thought it
OL,13,Fwas something being dropped.
OL,15,F"It was either a tray or a bullet."
OL,17,FWhen asked why this keeps happening to
OL,18,Fhim, he said he had studied
OL,19,Fassassinations and thought the
OL,20,Fpresidents who had the biggest impact
OL,21,Fwere the ones targeted.
