OL,3,CWhite House press dinner shooting:
OL,4,CTrump was remarkably calm and good
OL,5,Chumoured
OL,7,FHe was asked if he thought the alleged
OL,8,Fassailant named as 31-year-old Cole
OL,9,FTomas Allen, had political
OL,10,Fmotivations, he simply said "we'll be
OL,11,Fable to tell you that by tomorrow or
OL,12,Fthe next day".
OL,14,FThe president described him as "a sick
OL,15,Fperson", "a lone wolf" and a "whack
OL,16,Fjob".
