OL,3,CWhite House press dinner shooting:
OL,4,CTrump was remarkably calm and good
OL,5,Chumoured
OL,7,FHe paid tribute to the Secret Service
OL,8,Fteam which tackled the gunman,
OL,9,Fcomparing them to an action star. So
OL,10,Fended a remarkable press conference
OL,11,Ffollowing a dramatic and shocking
OL,12,Fevening.
OL,14,FAnother chapter in the long list of
OL,15,Fpresidential security incidents which
OL,16,Fthis time thankfully left no one dead.
OL,18,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,19,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,20,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,21,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
